I literally grew up with Tia and Tamera, watching them on TV and in their movies.  When I saw this on Amazon, even as an adult, I bought this to add to my collection.  Tia and Tamera are wonderful in this "Teen Twin Witch" sequel.  Adventure takes them to new places as they learn to control their magic.  I enjoyed this movie and am glad to own it now, so that my niece (and maybe daughter some day!!) can watch this with me.

I liked the first twitches, and this one picks up where it left off! who wouldn't want to be a witch? and have 2 homes! fantasy is the way to go! if you love these two actresses, it's a must see. you can really see yourself there. of course, that's the whole point. has some good behind the scenes stuff too. always a plus. also if you have a disney acct you can add points to it through this dvd. good thing.

Twitches too is such a good movie, I even think it's better than the first one. My favorite part was at the very end whenever Thantos was gone forever and Camerone and Alex had their dad back again - so sweet! Ileana and Karsh are so hilarious, they make a great couple! All I have to say about this movie is that, Twitches is really great, but Twitches Too is just as dazzling! Buy it - Twitches Too&Twitches - Betwitched Edition
I found this movie to be entertainment for the entire family.  Family fun in a box.

***HIGHLY RECOMMENDED*** I love easy fun family light family movies. Disney does a great job in that department. The movies were aired 2 consecutive years on Halloween. It's a lovely break from scary gross movies. Tia & Tamara are a breath of fresh air. This set of twins work. From what I understand they aren't "acting" very much in this movie rather they play roles that are close to their everyday life personalities. When you buy the DVD if you have a chance watch the special features. It tells you how to figure out who's who. How to tell them apart. The first movie "Twitches" should be seen before Twitches Too.
